\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In pia Jemes, k…ôn ilau n…ôt…® Sepeti mil. In kit r…ôha net…ôm tuelef r…ôha Iesu. K…ôn in et…ôm u it…ôm Iesu tolkeike p…®k. In t…ôm…ôte naoa m…®n u: Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r It…ôm Jon T…ôm…ôte, 1 Jon, 2 Jon, 3 Jon, ne Nol ∆èp…ôn.
