\v 6 Tol n…ôhlan, ok…ôm…ô kitat koat…ôper-ip…ôn lan, tol-p…ôn okol k…ôsot…ôk…ôike…ôn e nol…ôn rat m…®n. M…ôto net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm koat…ôk…ôike …ôh e nol…ôn rat m…®n, tol-p…ôn kot…ôruru ag…®n-…ôh in, m…ôsot…ôplan…ôn in.\f + \fr 3:6 \ft 1 Jon 3:9; 2:4; 5:18; 3 Jon 1:11\f*
