\v 9 Net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm k…ômotaiir wi m…®n motuwa nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n,\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Jon 1:13\f* ilat okol k…ôsot…ôk…ôike…ôn e nol…ôn rat,\f + \fr 3:9 \ft 1 Jon 5:18\f* m…ôto-inu ilat koatos niam…®t…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn o nat u, okol ilat k…ôsot…ôk…ôike…ôn e nol…ôn rat, m…ôto-inu ilat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 3:9 \ft N…®kuti nat tat…ôwi…ô noe-in at…®p…ôn noan. E suat…®p kiti…ôh …ôm, Uhg…®n tat…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhan niam…®t…ô e suah kit, k…ôn in tat…ôwi…ô tahmen e n…®kuti nat it…ôm k…ôm…ôfe e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha et…ômim un, k…ôn matoe in noan e nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, net…ômim m…®n u it…ôm k…ômotaiir wi m…®n motuwa nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n, ilat k…ôsot…ôk…ôike…ôn e nol…ôn rat.\f*
