\v 17 ?Ok…ôm…ô suah kit r…ôhan nat…®mnat tep…ôt k…ôn pian kit r…ôhan nat kit t…®k…ô, m…ôto in t…ôsas…ôkitun…ôn pian,\f + \fr 3:17 \ft Dut 15:7,8; Jem 2:15,16\f* m…ôsol…ôn nat ag…®n lan, nolkeike…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôhrol nulan mat…®g e suah u?\f + \fr 3:17 \ft 1 Jon 4:20\f*
