\v 6 M…ôto it…®mat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, net…ômim it…ôm kot…®tun Uhg…®n, ilat kot…ôt…ôl…®g-in it…®mat. M…ôto net…ômim it…ôm ilat s…ôn…ôm…ô nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n, ilat k…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn it…®mat.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Jon 8:47\f* O nat u, kitat okot…®tun …ôsas Narm…®n it…ôm tat…ôn pahrien,\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Jon 14:17\f* ne narm…®n it…ôm tateiu…ô.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Mak 13:5\f*
\s1 Nolkeike…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ne r…ôhatat
