\v 7 N…®kik m…®n, p…ôs kitat kotolkeike kitat m…®n,\f + \fr 4:7 \ft 1 Jon 3:11\f* m…ôto-inu nolkeike…ôn in tat…®s…®-p…ôn o Uhg…®n, k…ôn et…ôm tatol nolkeike…ôn, in t…ômaiir wi m…®n muwa n…ôt…® Uhg…®n kit,\f + \fr 4:7 \ft Jon 1:15\f* k…ôn t…®tun Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 4:7 \ft 1 Jon 2:4\f*
