\v 14 K…ônu it…®mat emot…ôplan r…ôk…®s k…ônu moat…ôn-iar…ôp\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Jon 15:27\f* m…ôm…ô Tata Uhg…®n in t…ômahl-ipa N…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô in Iosmeg…ôh r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Luk 2:11; Jon 3:17\f*
