\v 18 Et…ôm u t…ôrioah e nolkeike…ôn, okol t…ôs…ôgin…ôn Uhg…®n. M…ôto nolkeike…ôn pahrien u, it…ôm t…®natoe r…ôk…®s e n…®kitat, tat…ôhg-ir…ôk…®s n…ôg…®n…ôn,\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Rom 8:15\f* m…ôto-inu n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha nos…ôn nalp…®n…ôn tatol kitat koat…ôg…®n, k…ôn nat u tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô r…ôhan nolkeike…ôn t…ôsoe-in…ôn …ôh e n…®kitat.
\v 19 Kitat kotolkeike itat m…®n m…ôto-inun Uhg…®n t…ômaup…ôn molkeike itat.
\v 20 M…ôto ok…ôm…ô suah kit t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo ekolkeike Uhg…®n,‚Äù m…ôto tatet…ôhau …ôh pian,\f + \fr 4:20 \ft 1 Jon 2:9\f* in ieiu…ô.\f + \fr 4:20 \ft 1 Jon 1:6; 2:4\f* M…ôto-inu et…ôm t…ôsolkeike…ôn pian u in tatehm e n…®gan…ômt…®n,\f + \fr 4:20 \ft 1 Jon 3:17\f* okol t…ôsolkeike…ôn Uhg…®n, it…ôm in t…ôsehm…ôn.\f + \fr 4:20 \ft 1 Jon 4:12; Jon 1:18\f*
\v 21 K…ôn in t…ômos-ipa r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm itat m…ôm…ô et…ômim pah tolkeike Uhg…®n in ot…ôk…ôike molkeike m…®n pian.\f + \fr 4:21 \ft 1 Jon 2:7,9\f*
\c 5
\s1 Kitat koatol win m…ôto-inu kitat koatahat…ôt…ô e Iesu
\m 
\v 1 Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Jon 3:15\f* e Iesu m…ôm…ô in Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, suah u inu, in n…ôt…® Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Jon 1:13; 1 Jon 2:22; 1 Jon 2:23\f* k…ôn et…ômim it…ôm in tolkeike tata kit, in tolkeike m…®n nen…ôt…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 5:1 \ft 1 Jon 2:23\f*
\v 2 K…ôn kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô kotolkeike Uhg…®n k…ônu moatol n…ôwian,\f + \fr 5:2 \ft 1 Jon 2:3\f* k…ônu okotolkeike m…®n nen…ôt…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 5:2 \ft 1 Jon 3:14\f*
\v 3 M…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô kotolkeike Uhg…®n, n…®p…ôt…®n un, okotol noan,\f + \fr 5:3 \ft Jon 14:15\f* k…ôn r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn otahmen e katipa it…ôm taluk-aluk …ôm.\f + \fr 5:3 \ft Mat 11:30\f*
\v 4 Net…ôm kotaiir e Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Jon 1:13\f* ilat koatol win e nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn. K…ônu nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhatat in tatos-ipa n…ôsan…ôn…ôn o nol…ô win e nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.
\v 5 ?Pah m…®n un ilat koat…ôtul …ôskas…®k motol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u? Ilat …ôm un, net…ôm kotatahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô Iesu in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n.
\s1 Iaru…ôsan k…®s…®l k…ôt…ôhalol …ôp // Iesu Kristo k…ôm kitat
\p 
\v 6 Iesu Kristo, in et…ôm u it…ôm t…ômuwa, k…ôn n…ôhau ne n…®tan\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Jon 19:34,35\f* k…ôtioal …ôp in k…ôm itat. S…ôn…ôm…ô n…ôhau …ôm it…ôm tatol …ôp in, m…ôto n…ôhau ne n…®tan.
\v 7 Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n in t…ôtaru…ôsan n…ôghat…ôn mil u r…ôha n…ôhau ne n…®ta, mat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôto-inu Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n in n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Jon 14:17\f*
\v 8 K…ôn nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn k…®s…®l k…ôt…ôhalaru…ôsan il…ôhal m…®n. Il…ôhal un, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, ne n…ôhau, ne n…®ta. K…ôn il…ôhal u, k…ôt…ôhaleg…ôhan-in m…ôt…ôhalol …ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhal…ôhal m…®n.
\v 9 Nian m…®n, kitat koat…ôto n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm net…ômim koat…ôn-iar…ôp, motahat…ôt…ô elat.\f + \fr 5:9 \ft Jon 5:33,34\f* M…ôto nian Uhg…®n tat…ôn-iar…ôp nat kit, in iahgin tapr…ôk…®s, k…ôn kitat okot…®tun nahat…ôt…ô…ôn t…ôhm…®n m…®n e r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, m…ôto-inu in Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:9 \ft Mat 3:16,17; Jon 5:32,37; 8:17,18\f* k…ôn in tat…ôtul-ar…ôp o N…ôt…®n.
\p 
\v 10 Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôtahat…ôt…ô e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, in tat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e n…®kin o n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. M…ôto et…ômim it…ôm t…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn u r…ôha Uhg…®n, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n in ieiueiu…ô …ôm,\f + \fr 5:10 \ft Jon 3:33; 1 Jon 1:10\f* m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôtul-ar…ôp o N…ôt…®n, m…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm in, m…ôto in t…ôs…ôn…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn lan.
\v 11 K…ônu n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp o N…ôt…®n, in tol nulan. Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n\f + \fr 5:11 \ft Mat 25:46\f* k…ôm itat, k…ônu n…ômeg…ôh…ôn u, katos o N…ôt…®n.\f + \fr 5:11 \ft Jon 1:4\f*
\v 12 Et…ôm tatos N…ôt…®n, in tatos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. M…ôto et…ôm t…ôsos…ôn N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, in t…ôsos…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.\f + \fr 5:12 \ft Jon 3:15,16,36\f*
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn
