\v 13 Iat…ôte n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u k…ôm it…ômat net…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô it…ômat nakotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.\f + \fr 5:13 \ft 1 Jon 5:11\f*
\v 14 P…ôs k…ôsot…ôg…®n…ôn,\f + \fr 5:14 \ft Efes 3:12; 1 Jon 3:21\f* m…ôto kot…ôskas…®k o n…ôtap…ôh-in…ôn nat kit e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu kot…®tun m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn u inu, tatem …ôskas…®k itat. Nian okot…ôtap…ôh-in nat kit k…ôm in it…ôm t…ôw…®r e r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn, k…ôn in ot…ôto r…ôhatat n…ôfak…ôn.\f + \fr 5:14 \ft Mat 7:7\f*
\v 15 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô kot…®tun m…ôm…ô in ot…ôto itat, k…ôn nat naka okoteasi…ô-in-p…ôn, k…ôn k…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô okotos.\f + \fr 5:15 \ft 1 King 3:12\f*
\p 
\v 16 Ok…ôm…ô kotehm piatat kit tatol nol…ôn rat, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô nol…ôn rat it…ôm t…®tun nit-ip…ôn…ôn e n…®m…®s…ôn, ik onak…ôfak ron, k…ôn Uhg…®n otos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn k…ôm suah u.\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Jem 5:15\f* M…ôto nol…ôn rat kit …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm tatit-ip…ôn it…ôm e n…®m…®s…ôn,\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Hip 6:4-6; 10:26\f* k…ôn io es…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôfak o net…ôm m…®n it…ôm koatol nol…ôn …ôh.\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Jer 7:16; 14:11\f*\f + \fr 5:16 \ft E ves u, ne ves 17, Jon tat…ôghat-in t…ôfag…ô rat it…ôm tatit-ip…ôn it…ôm e n…®m…®s…ôn. Jon tat…ôghat-in t…ôfag…ô rat it…ôm k…ôt…ôuhlin m…ôntaat…ôm o Kristo ne net…ôhau…ôn r…ôhan net…ômim. Nol…ôn rat m…®n …ôh, tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô net…ôm koatol ilat k…ôsotos…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n, k…ônu m…ôs…®n m…®n u m…ôm…ô narm…®lat t…®n…®m…®s. Nat u inu, Jon tat…ôn …ôhag-…ôhag k…ôm itat e 1 Jon 5:12 ne 1 Jon 3:14. // E Mat 12:31-32 tat…ôghat-in t…ôfag…ô rat u, n…ôn rat…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.\f*
\v 17 Nol…ôn rat m…®n rafin un, in t…ôfag…ô rat,\f + \fr 5:17 \ft 1 Jon 3:4\f* k…ôn m…ôto t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm k…ôsotit-ip…ôn…ôn it…ôm e n…®m…®s…ôn.\f + \fr 5:17 \ft 1 Jon 5:16; 1 Jon 2:1\f*
\p 
\v 18 Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô et…ôm t…ôtaiir e Uhg…®n\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Jon 1:13\f* t…ôs…ôk…ôike…ôn e t…ôfag…ô rat, m…ôto-inu N…ôt…® Uhg…®n tat…ôm…®k …ôtain w…®r in, k…ôn et…ôm rat u Setan, t…ôruru nek…ôn.\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Jon 14:30\f*
\v 19 Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô kitat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n,\f + \fr 5:19 \ft 1 Jon 4:6\f* m…ôto net…ômim r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn rafin, ilat u kotat…®g e nelm…® Setan.\f + \fr 5:19 \ft Jon 12:31; 14:30; 17:15\f*
\v 20 Kitat kot…®tun m…®n m…ôm…ô N…ôt…® Uhg…®n t…ômuwa k…ôn mos-ipa nenat…®g…ôn k…ôm itat,\f + \fr 5:20 \ft Luk 24:45\f* m…ôm…ô kitat okot…®tun in, u in n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 5:20 \ft Jon 17:3\f* K…ônu kitat koat…ôtul-p…ôn e Uhg…®n u in n…®pahrien…ôn, m…ôto-inu kitat koat…ôtul-p…ôn e N…ôt…®n Iesu Kristo. In un, in Uhg…®n pahrien, k…ôn in n…ôuk…ôt…® n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.\f + \fr 5:20 \ft 1 Jon 5:11\f*
\p 
\v 21 Nen…ôt…®k m…®n, otag…®m r…ôk…®s o nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm okotos n…ôme Uhg…®n e n…®kit…ômat.\f + \fr 5:21 \ft 1 Kor 10:14; 1 Tes 1:9\f*\f + \fr 5:21 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúonakag…®m o narm…® nat m…®n,‚Äù m…ôto Jon tat…ôghat-in t…ôfag…ô rat, m…ôm…ô in tahmen e narm…® nat, m…ôto ok…ôm…ô kotolkeike r…ôhatat t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n tapr…ôk…®s-in Uhg…®n, k…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat in tatos n…ôme Uhg…®n e n…®kitat.\f* 
